summary: The document is an identification form associated with the JFK Assassination System, focusing on an investigation into Manuel Marti. It mentions Juanita Reyes as a character reference for Marti and details efforts to locate and interview Reyes in New York City, including checks of telephone directories and calls that revealed changes and unlisted numbers. The document is noted as unclassified but released with deletions, suggesting some information was withheld.
key_findings: The investigation is part of the JFK Assassination System and centers on Manuel Marti.
Juanita Reyes is identified as a character reference for Marti, with unsuccessful attempts to locate her in New York City.
Efforts to find Reyes involved consulting telephone directories and making calls, which indicated her number was changed or unlisted.
The document is unclassified but contains deletions, implying certain details were redacted before release.
